 Mar 2024 10:15:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-25/ty-article-opinion/.premium/feeling-endangered-an-israeli-prescription-for-killing-with-no-criticism-or-oversight/0000018e-74fc-d829-a3ef-74fdbece0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙卫生部：最后一天有 107 人死亡；以色列国防军称“500 名恐怖分子在希法被捕”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-25/ty-article-live/huge-mistake-kamala-harris-ruling-out-nothing-if-israel-invades-rafah/0000018e-73b3-ddf4-a3de-7bb383c00000</link><description>八枚火箭弹从加沙向阿什杜德发射 ■ 人质家属参加并抗议耶路撒冷普珥节游行 ■ 哈马斯消息人士：“以色列对希法医院的攻势不可低估” ■ 根据以色列国防军的数据，自周五以来，已有 30 名士兵在战斗中受伤</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 04:15:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-25/ty-article-live/huge-mistake-kamala-harris-ruling-out-nothing-if-israel-invades-rafah/0000018e-73b3-ddf4-a3de-7bb383c00000</guid></item><item><title>战时内阁职位未能实现后，萨尔可能退出政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-25/ty-article/.premium/saar-likely-to-quiet-government-after-war-cabinet-position-fails-to-materialize/0000018e-7237-ddf4-a3de-7ab70eee0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡愿意让萨尔在战时内阁中占有一席之地，但国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本格维尔要求“平等”条款并获得一个管理战争的席位，这是一个主要问题。利库德集团一名高级官员表示，“除非出现意外，萨尔即将下台”</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 03:59:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-25/ty-article/.premium/saar-likely-to-quiet-government-after-war-cabinet-position-fails-to-materialize/0000018e-7237-ddf4-a3de-7ab70eee0000</guid></item><item><title>“我们来这里不仅仅是为了操哈马斯”：以色列军国主义如何接管在线约会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/were-not-only-here-to-fuck-hamas-how-israeli-militarism-took-over-online-dating/0000018e-60aa-d27e-a7af-7aeec5b00000</link><description>为什么以色列士兵将自己在加沙家里或与巴勒斯坦被拘留者的照片上传到他们的约会资料中？ 9 月 11 日之后，除了让美国消防员成为英雄的“统一效应”之外，一些专家表示，约会应用程序上出现的暴力军国主义正在导致以色列社会线上线下出现令人不安的趋势。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 20:41:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/were-not-only-here-to-fuck-hamas-how-israeli-militarism-took-over-online-dating/0000018e-60aa-d27e-a7af-7aeec5b00000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦红新月会表示，以色列军队包围了汗尤尼斯的两家医院</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-red-crescent-idf-besieges-two-hospitals-in-khan-yunis/0000018e-7219-ddf4-a3de-7abb4e3e0000</link><description>据巴勒斯坦红新月会称，以色列士兵没有进入医院，但双方附近发生了交火。以色列国防军称已收到有关阿迈勒大院内恐怖分子的准确情报</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 20:35:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-red-crescent-idf-besieges-two-hospitals-in-khan-yunis/0000018e-7219-ddf4-a3de-7abb4e3e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长预计将拒绝在高等法院为内塔尼亚胡豁免正统派的法案草案辩护</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-expected-to-refuse-to-defend-netanyahu-draft-bill-that-exempts-haredim/0000018e-71df-d477-abbf-f7dfa8890000</link><description>总检察长巴哈拉夫-米亚拉澄清，如果上届政府不延长征召极端正统派的决定，并且不通过新法案，犹太学院的学生将被征召入以色列军队</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 20:27:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-expected-to-refuse-to-defend-netanyahu-draft-bill-that-exempts-haredim/0000018e-71df-d477-abbf-f7dfa8890000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长的真正目标是推翻内塔尼亚胡政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-defense-chiefs-real-aim-is-to-bring-down-netanyahus-government/0000018e-71d8-ddf4-a3de-79fa0c0d0000</link><description>国防部长约阿夫·加兰特（Yoav Gallant）并不为极端正统派逃避征兵而烦恼。但由于政府未能为加沙战争设定明确的目标，他唯一的选择就是试图策划联盟的垮台</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 20:19:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-defense-chiefs-real-aim-is-to-bring-down-netanyahus-government/0000018e-71d8-ddf4-a3de-79fa0c0d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列妇女被枪杀，目标可能是她的丈夫，因谋杀罪受审</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-woman-shot-dead-target-likely-her-husband-on-trial-for-murder/0000018e-71b4-df85-afde-f7f527920000</link><description>这名以色列妇女的丈夫自 2018 年被指控犯有谋杀罪以来一直被软禁，原定于周日出庭作证。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 19:09:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-woman-shot-dead-target-likely-her-husband-on-trial-for-murder/0000018e-71b4-df85-afde-f7f527920000</guid></item><item><title>以色列阿拉伯议员因“点赞”帖子而受到猛烈抨击，指控以色列和美国控制的伊斯兰国伤害穆斯林</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-arab-lawmaker-slammed-for-liking-post-alleging-isis-run-by-israel-and-u-s/0000018e-7147-ddf4-a3de-79f712770000</link><description>以色列阿拉伯议会议员艾哈迈德·提比 (Ahmad Tibi) 表示，“点赞”X 上有争议的帖子——一名伊斯兰传教士将周五莫斯科恐怖袭击归咎于以色列情报部门和美国——是“错误点赞”</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 17:42:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-arab-lawmaker-slammed-for-liking-post-alleging-isis-run-by-israel-and-u-s/0000018e-7147-ddf4-a3de-79f712770000</guid></item><item><title>马尔默有欧洲歌唱大赛热潮。它的犹太社区正在感受到热度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-03-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/only-teardrops-malmo-has-the-eurovision-fever-its-jewish-community-is-feeling-the-heat/0000018e-708a-d8e8-a9de-7cbb53170000</link><description>在举办大型歌曲比赛前几周对瑞典第三大城市的访问表明，将巴勒斯坦事业推上欧洲最大舞台的准备工作正在紧锣密鼓地进行。 “我认识的人在公共场合摘下带有大卫之星的项链”</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 17:41:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-03-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/only-teardrops-malmo-has-the-eurovision-fever-its-jewish-community-is-feeling-the-heat/0000018e-708a-d8e8-a9de-7cbb53170000</guid></item><item><title>你需要知道的，第 170 天：官员表示，以色列在停战谈判中的问题上持灵活态度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/what-you-need-to-know-day-170-israel-flexible-on-issues-in-truce-talks-official-says/0000018e-716f-ddf4-a3de-79ff9e630000</link><description>美国副总统哈里斯表示，她不排除以色列在拉法发动攻势的“后果” ■ 以色列国防军称已开始在汗尤尼斯开展行动 ■ 高级官员表示，以色列在与哈马斯停火谈判的两个主要问题上表现出了灵活性 ■ 以色列近东救济工程处负责人表示，将不再批准近东救济工程处向加沙北部运送粮食车队 ■ 数十个非政府组织表示，以色列不遵守美国国家安全备忘录 ■ 战争结束 170 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 17:15:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/what-you-need-to-know-day-170-israel-flexible-on-issues-in-truce-talks-official-says/0000018e-716f-ddf4-a3de-79ff9e630000</guid></item><item><title>国家安全部长本-格维尔非法发布因涉嫌袭击而被捕的以色列未成年人的照片</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-illegally-publishes-photo-of-israeli-minor-arrested-for-assault/0000018e-7112-ddf4-a3de-79b277750000</link><description>以色列法律禁止公布涉嫌犯罪的未成年人的照片或详细信息，并规定最高可判处一年监禁</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 16:12:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-illegally-publishes-photo-of-israeli-minor-arrested-for-assault/0000018e-7112-ddf4-a3de-79b277750000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布在加沙 Al-Shifa 医院战斗中丧生的以色列士兵姓名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/idf-names-israeli-soldier-killed-in-combat-at-gazas-al-shifa-hospital/0000018e-70fb-d1c9-af8f-7efbc8270000</link><description>上士利奥尔·拉维夫周六在加沙北部的希法医院附近被杀，他的父母和三个兄弟姐妹幸存下来。战友们形容他是一位优秀、有道德、谦虚的军人</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 15:19:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/idf-names-israeli-soldier-killed-in-combat-at-gazas-al-shifa-hospital/0000018e-70fb-d1c9-af8f-7efbc8270000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨威胁要退出内塔尼亚胡战争政府，因为该法案草案豁免了极端正统派</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-dm-says-wont-support-netanyahus-draft-proposal-that-exempts-haredim/0000018e-706a-ddf4-a3de-78fa0d140000</link><description>以色列国防部长约夫·加兰特在周日启程前往华盛顿时也表示反对内塔尼亚胡总理起草的法案大纲，该法案大纲禁止极端正统派入伍</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 14:35:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-dm-says-wont-support-netanyahus-draft-proposal-that-exempts-haredim/0000018e-706a-ddf4-a3de-78fa0d140000</guid></item><item><title>吐槽问题：以色列公司开发出第一个基于唾液的妊娠测试</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/spit-at-the-question-israeli-company-develops-first-saliva-based-pregnancy-test/0000018e-701a-d1c9-af8f-7ebbb5b30000</link><description>这种名为 Salistick 的家庭测试可以在月经推迟的第一天就检测出 β-hCG 激素，而月经推迟十天后，这是大多数家庭尿液检测的标准，并且 96准确率百分比</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 12:35:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/spit-at-the-question-israeli-company-develops-first-saliva-based-pregnancy-test/0000018e-701a-d1c9-af8f-7ebbb5b30000</guid></item><item><title>犹太人为什么要盛装庆祝普珥节？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/why-do-jews-dress-up-for-purim/0000017f-f77a-d044-adff-f7fb75f00000</link><description>借来的东西，借的东西？这一习俗似乎起源于 13 世纪的意大利，庆祝活动和化装舞会在忏悔星期二期间不断升级</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 12:27:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/why-do-jews-dress-up-for-purim/0000017f-f77a-d044-adff-f7fb75f00000</guid></item><item><title>“印度炸药”：在加沙，以色列国防军使用了 70 年前用于训练的弹药和炮弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-24/ty-article/a-huge-mess-in-gaza-idf-used-70-year-old-munitions-and-shells-intended-for-training/0000018e-5db4-d4b2-afcf-dfb626a90000</link><description>试图将弹药、非正规货物和“印度炸药”保存在分解的麻袋中，造成了后勤和行动上的噩梦，使炮兵部队难以协助作战部队，并增加了出错和错过目标的风险</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 12:22:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-24/ty-article/a-huge-mess-in-gaza-idf-used-70-year-old-munitions-and-shells-intended-for-training/0000018e-5db4-d4b2-afcf-dfb626a90000</guid></item><item><title>战争结束五个月后，约旦河西岸和加沙地带的居民为哈马斯的袭击辩护</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/five-months-into-the-war-residents-of-both-the-west-bank-and-gaza-justify-hamas-attack/0000018e-65ac-da37-a3ff-77bc473e0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦民意调查显示，加沙人对袭击的支持率从三个月前的 57% 大幅上升至 71%</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 10:55:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-24/ty-article/.premium/five-months-into-the-war-residents-of-both-the-west-bank-and-gaza-justify-hamas-attack/0000018e-65ac-da37-a3ff-77bc473e0000</guid></item></channel></rss>